arted recording and releasing songs on his [[MySpace]] page in 2006, by 2008 he had gained a small local fanbase in New Delhi and racked up features with artists in the U.S and Canada.<ref name=\"UK 2017\" /> His first shot of success came with the release of the music video for \"Kaisa Mera Desh\" in 2010,<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mid-day.com/articles/desi-rapper-slamming-cwg-is-a-hit/97263|title=Desi rapper slamming CWG is a hit|work=mid-day|access-date=2017-12-26}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.mensxp.com/entertainment/must-watch/3151-yeh-kaisa-mera-desh-young-prozpekts-rant-against-the-commonwealth-games.html|title='Yeh Kaisa Mera Desh: - Young Prozpekt's Rant against the Commonwealth Games|work=Men's XP|access-date=2017-12-26|language=en}}</ref> becoming the first Indian hip hop song on [[YouTube]] and earning a #2 ranking as one of the most watched music videos in India overnight following its release.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://indiatoday.intoday.in/story/hip-hop-hustle/1/298301.html|title=Hip hop hustle|access-date=2017-12-26}}</ref> He also released a song titled \"Vijay\" in collaboration with international NGO [[Save The Children]] in 2013.<ref>{{cite web |title=Young Prozpekt playing for change |url=https://www.hindustantimes.com/music/young-prozpekt-playing-for-change/story-Qr1RKZrGhrS8jn9KHFHoPL.html}}</ref>\n\nAfter sporadic underground releases, Kaul switched from Prozpekt to his current stage name KR$NA after signing a record deal with [[Universal Music]] in 2013.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.radioandmusic.com/biz/music/artiste/contrabands-signs-indie-artist-rapper-and-hip-hop-musician-krsna|title=Contrabands signs on indie artist, rapper and hip-hop musician - KRSNA|access-date=2017-12-26}}</ref> In May 2014, he released his debut album ''Sellout'', an all-English effort on Universal Music with its lead single \"Last Night\" peaking at #5 on the [[Vh1|Vh1 Music Charts]] in India.<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.radioandmusic.com/nod